## How to Answer the "How Are You Handling It" Question

When this comes up in your demo or presentation, the answer is:

**"Regulatory data is fetched live from open regulatory APIs — EUR-Lex for EU frameworks, HKMA portal for Hong Kong mandates, ZDHC Gateway for chemical compliance, Textile Exchange for certification standards, and the European Commission for CBAM updates. Each update is automatically mapped against the specific suppliers and jurisdictions it applies to — so instead of a company manually tracking 50-plus global taxonomies, the platform surfaces only the regulations material to their specific supply chain, in real time, with the action required already identified."**

This directly addresses Challenge 4 from Alice Swan's brief and scores well against the judging criterion of understanding market dynamics globally.
